{
  "stem": "12003.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when you're young, you hear the stories, but I don't think that they are as penetrating as when you have the full awareness and maturity about life.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't tell my children my story until they were a little bit older.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't want to frighten them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know how to start telling them my story.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted them to be strong, and confident, and have trust in human beings-- in people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The disappointment, for me, was very great, too, and still is, in human beings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I continue to have faith.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I'm still disappointed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When-- I thought I will be freed when I was free.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I thought I find freedom for all people-- that I wouldn't see any suffering and starvation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it's not so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There is still a lot of suffering, a lot of prejudice-- a lot of hurt-- hunger in this world.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the purpose of me sitting here today-- which, by the way, is-- is certainly not an enjoyment for me-- so people can know what happened.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It didn't leave me scarred.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I am scarred.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I, uh-- [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] --I don't want to talk about it, because I believe in better world to come.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] But it leaved us all scarred.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[CRYING] You know, I'm not emotional for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I am emotional for those-- [CRYING] --I feel emotional and sorry for those that didn't make it-- and for many of those that are scarred.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My own mother-- she never recuperated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "She functions.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she goes from day to day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But to lose her family, to be uprooted, it's a horrible thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I am very grateful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I appreciate what I have.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I appreciate this country.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
